<!--=============== Melee ====================-->
  <ThingDef ParentName="EGOArmorBase">
	<defName>EGO_Armor_Shell_Melee</defName>
    <label>EGO Shell(Berserker)</label>
    <description>Specially gestated amalgam Shell, excellent protects the owner. Designed for use by Undyings. Amalgams are hybrids of EGO seed and Obsidia technology.\n\nThis modification improve melee combat stats and modified with the addition of a Smokepop pack.\n\nThe item's quality levels can be reset using an EGO Seed.</description>
